Additional Notes: Transitions to Jab 2 as early as frame 5
Transitions to Jab 3 as early as frame 6
Head intangibility on frame 9-13. Charge hold is frame 6
If you land before firing, it will fire on frame 6 of landing. Advantage is that shot.

On hit endlag is 18 or 32 total if you landed during that 18 frame animation. Total frames is 
80 in the air, 95 on level ground. 41 landing lag is consistent as long as you land during the 
80 frame animation. Invulnerable on frame 18-22.
Invulnerable on frame 8-10 on the ground. Total frames assumes level ground.
Invulnerable on frame 6-8 in the air
Invincible on frame 4-8 on the ground. 1-7 in the air.
